column11: I got a great price on an audi but when I went in for maintenance they told me that certain things were not covered that I was told would be covered.
The entire experience from start to finish was extremely professional and one that makes a important decision a lot easier.
My experience at Atlantic Audi was nothing but horrible! The sales associate I dealt with  was rude, unpleasant, and only cared about selling a car.

I was SO turned off by this guy, I walked out immediately following our conversation about the 1st car. I would have expected that type or behavior at Tony's Used Car Sales - not at an Audi dealership.
It is unreal how UNPROFESSIONAL and CLASSLESS those people are.I feel sorry for Audi(and anyone else who wasted time with them).
Nicie sales rep. He was very helpful I will recommend family and friends to audi anytime I love my car. It's runs very well.
The salesmen were great but they did not have as wide of a selection that I had hoped for, still a great experience
They wanted to squeeze me for every dollar I had. They seemed entiteled to  my money. I will not be going back to this place

Horrible customer service and very rude, unprofessional staff. I will never take my car to this dealer again and would never purchase another car from them either. They should not have a staff like them standing behind the Audi name.
The atmosphere was warm and welcoming and the staff made you feel like they knew you.. beautiful showroom and waiting area. Huge selection on hand.
Greg helped me find a car that suited my personality and needs much more than the 5 series. I've had nothing but a positive experience during my dealings with those at Faulkner.
Great sales experience, got a car at a great price, however I had to take it in for a problem and they were not as helpful as the first day I came in
Greg helped me find a car that suited my personality and needs much more than the 5 series. I've had nothing but a positive experience during my dealings with those at Faulkner.
Everything is slow in this dealership. Response through emails or phone calls are slow. When I actually decided to go there to discuss pricing, it took hours for every other offers presented.

He did everything he could to make the buying process efficient. We are very thankful. There was absolutely no pressure and we were able to test drive the cars we wanted and make a reasonable decision.
I absolutely love the car, the car is great, but I would not go back to this place to buy any other car as the maintenance issues after the fact were not very convenient
Make sure financing gives you paperwork and you read through it thoroughly, especially if you are a first time buyer they will try to take advantage.
They were very friendly but their selection was a little on the pricey side. They could stand to decrease their prices and maybe I would think about buying a car

the rep was very nice and gave me great advice, and direction in my car buying journey, but the 20 yr. they had me talk to at the beginning almost turned me away. Some better training could be used here

While the staff was fairly friendly, they seemed a little unprepared for my appointment. They forgot which cars I wanted to check out, and didn’t tailor well. I believe they were well intentioned but they did not have great preparation
it was my first time at Apple. He took them time to understand my situation and provided with multiple options at a good price.
It was a normal car buying experience, the saleperson was competent, but offered no extra assistance. It seemed like he didn’t like his job
Wide selection of cars, they had multiple brands that I was looking into

The entire experience, from the initial visit (no appointment), to the test drive and negotiation, to financing and delivery were great. Dennis is a pleasure to work with and isn't afraid to suggest things you hadn't thought of.
Once I got to see a sales representative they were great, but they did not do a good job of planning as I waited in the lounge area for a while

I had a great car buying experience however I waited almost 2hts for an oil change, received no car wash and some left coca cola soda in my car as if they had their lunch in it. Not the type of service or experience I'm used to.
Dealing with him was a pleasure.He answered all my questions on my new purchase. But I liked the fact we spoke and touched on a more personal level
Dishonest on price of car and deal made wasn't what was on contract. Charge my cc as a deposit and then refused to refund deposit
The only thing I wills ay is for the salepeople to work on their people skils. While they had a great selection, they need to tailor to our needs better than they did.
Jimmy was great exceeded my expectations in every way was able to find a car for me for less than I ever wanted to pay.
